    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >缔造文明，面对时代的考验</h2><br><strong>探索史前地球，大陆正在漂移，最后的大冰期即将到来，凶猛的食肉动物在陆上游荡。带领你的部落克服艰难险境，为了生存而做出最大的努力。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >残酷的星球考验生存能力</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/9d4543704982dde1fd09118e2f11ef3b.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/9d4543704982dde1fd09118e2f11ef3b.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/9d4543704982dde1fd09118e2f11ef3b.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>置身史前地球严酷的自然之中，引领部落平安熬过春夏秋冬。<br></li><li>抵御野兽、干旱与寒冬，保护部落，确保他们安心无忧。<br></li><li>采集食物与资源，保障氏族温饱、健康。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弱肉强食</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/725c50acf74c1cb783fd0b5edd927570.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/725c50acf74c1cb783fd0b5edd927570.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/725c50acf74c1cb783fd0b5edd927570.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>捕杀远古野兽，迁徙途中也能发现新的动物。<br></li><li>六角地图方格，为氏族之间的战斗提供了战术设计的空间。<br></li><li>简介窗口供你了解各个地区生活的史前动物。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >促进部落发展</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/12c2b0f014e410ff1124d4ed31d96a39.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/12c2b0f014e410ff1124d4ed31d96a39.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/12c2b0f014e410ff1124d4ed31d96a39.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>制作工具和兵器，搭建遮风挡雨的场所，令你的部落发展成为开化的社会。<br></li><li>研究原始科技，因地制宜，制作新的工具。<br></li><li>见证人类的历史发展，或者创造你自己的历史。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >推动文明演化</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/d8d0f2db823cbd1de58252c3268893fa.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/d8d0f2db823cbd1de58252c3268893fa.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/d8d0f2db823cbd1de58252c3268893fa.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发现自己的语言，为部落构建身份认同，团结族人。<br></li><li>创造基础的宗教观念，进而建立属于自己的精神信仰。<br></li><li>打造自己的文化，父系还是母系，多偶还是单偶，诸如此类的路线都由你来决定。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >迁往新的地区</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/0486055686587550fa6ba37ba6cf82c0.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/0486055686587550fa6ba37ba6cf82c0.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/0486055686587550fa6ba37ba6cf82c0.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>迁往地球其他地方，甚至直面最为恶劣的气候条件。无论遇到怎样的自然环境，都要努力生存。<br></li><li>迎接或者损失部族和族人，巧妙规划，让每一个部族和每一个人都充分发挥作用。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/fa9063b52c26f0bbde9c1613ab75e042.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/fa9063b52c26f0bbde9c1613ab75e042.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/fa9063b52c26f0bbde9c1613ab75e042.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>部落乃至人类的未来完全由你掌握，你们能否生存下去，发展壮大呢？<br><br><strong>立刻体验试玩版，将正式版加入愿望单</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1725035002\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769130/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1725035002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
